---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';

const APPLY_URL = "https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSegkqZvXTR7PB1O6yYSMVDGANMRMOmfegGPCnI6StZtIqmcgw/viewform";
---

<Base title="Apply — Wayfinders" description="Apply for a Wayfinders cohort.">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Apply</h1>

    <aside class="highlight-box" aria-label="Cohort status">
      <p class="highlight-heading"><strong>Next cohort</strong></p>
      <p class="highlight-body">Applications are open. Read what we'll ask below, then start your application at the bottom of the page.</p>
    </aside>

    <h2>What we'll ask you</h2>
    <p>The application takes about five minutes. Honest answers are more useful than impressive ones.</p>

    <h3>About you</h3>
    <p>Your name, email, where in the UK you're based, roughly how old you are, what you do for work, and what church or tradition shapes your faith.</p>

    <h3>The decision</h3>
    <p>Three questions:</p>
    <ol>
      <li><strong>What's the decision in front of you?</strong> One paragraph. The actual decision, not the polished version.</li>
      <li><strong>Why is this decision in front of you now?</strong> What's changed? A trigger, a season ending, a question that won't go away?</li>
      <li><strong>What would "good" look like at the end of eight weeks?</strong></li>
    </ol>

    <h3>Honest checks</h3>
    <p>We'll ask whether you're currently exploring ordained ministry (if so, this isn't the right fit), whether you're in a personal crisis right now (we'd rather you got the right help first), and whether you can commit to all five sessions over eight weeks.</p>

    <h2>What happens next</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>You apply.</li>
      <li>Ben reads every application personally.</li>
      <li>Within five working days: a yes, a "let's have a quick chat," or an honest no with a better pointer.</li>
      <li>If accepted, you're matched with a mentor and introduced before the cohort starts.</li>
    </ol>

    <h2>Who gets in</h2>
    <p>
      Cohorts are small &mdash; 6 to 8 people. We're looking for a mix of sectors, ages, and traditions. The application isn't competitive; it's about fit. If the timing or shape isn't right for you, we'll say so kindly and invite you to a future cohort.
    </p>

    <h2>Before you apply</h2>
    <p>
      Please read the <a href="/principles">principles of engagement</a>. They're the conditions of taking part, not aspirations. The application form asks you to confirm you've read them.
    </p>

    <div class="cta-block">
      <a href={APPLY_URL} class="btn" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Start your application<span class="sr-only"> (opens in a new tab)</span></a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  ol {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin: 0.75rem 0 1rem;
  }
  ol li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }

  .cta-block {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .coming-soon {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    font-style: italic;
  }
</style>
